    <briefdescription>
<para>Command to request despawning of a GameObject. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1spawn_1_1commands_1_1DespawnCommand" kindref="compound">DespawnCommand</ref> is a WorldCommand that requests the deactivation and return of a GameObject to its pool. The command identifies the target entity by its handle and specifies the spawn profile for pool return.</para>
<para>The command is dispatched to a DespawnCommandDispatcher which forwards it to the appropriate <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1spawn_1_1SpawnManager" kindref="compound">SpawnManager</ref> for deferred processing.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1spawn_1_1commands_1_1SpawnCommand" kindref="compound">SpawnCommand</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para>DespawnCommandDispatcher </para>
</simplesect>
